game.}) 16... gxf5 (16... exf5 17. Nxd5 Qxd5 18. Ng5 $16) 17. Ne2 Nb6 18. b3
Rac8 19. Nf4 $16) 16. b3 ({I was in no hurry to win a pawn:} 16. Nxd5 Qxd5 17.
Ng5 Qxa2 18. Rxc6 Nd5 $14) 16... Qd7 17. g4 Rfc8 (17... b4 18. Ne2 Bxe2 19.
Rxe2 Rfc8 20. Rec2 Na7 21. Bf1 $16 {The endgame will be very difficult for
