16. Rad1 Rfd8 17. Bf2 $14) 13... cxd4 14. cxd4 Qd7 15. Qa3 Rfd8 16. Rac1 $14
Na5 {This attempt at counterplay only wastes time.} 17. b4 Nac6 18. Qb3 $16 {
Strikovic,A (2554)-Bogosavljevic,B (2551) Vrnjacka Banja 2010 (1-0, 54)}) 13.
dxc5 {Black now has a familiar choice.} dxc5 (13... bxc5 14. Na3 Qa5 15. Qxa5
