d3 Bd7 (11... Qd5 {is parried with} 12. e4 fxe4 13. Bg2 $16) 12. Bf4 {As
mentioned before White has to be ready to give back the pawn in order to
complete his development.} Qb4+ 13. Qd2 Qxd2+ (13... Qxb2 14. Qe3+ Kf7 15. Be5
Qb4+ (15... Re8 16. Bxb2 Rxe3 17. Kf2 Re8 18. h3 $14) 16. Qd2 Qxd2+ 17. Kxd2
$14 {The two bishops offer White the better chances in the endgame.}) 14. Kxd2
