16... Kf7 17. dxe4 Nd7 18. Bc4+) (16... Kf8 17. dxe4 Nd7 18. Bd3 $16) 17. Bg2
Nc5 18. b4 O-O-O 19. Kc3 Na4+ 20. Kb3 $16) 16. h4 O-O-O ({During the game I
