19. Bxd3 $16) 17. Kc3 Nc5 18. Be2 fxe4 19. d4 ({I refrained from} 19. Bxg4+ {
because I did not wish to exchange the bishops so soon.} Bd7 20. Bxd7+ Rxd7 21.
