sort of commitment. Had White played h2-h3 instead, he could now have reacted
with} 10. c4 {with similar play as in Line 21.}) 10... Qc7 ({Black could delay
his queen's development as the pin along the long diagonal is not dangerous:} 
10... Nc6 11. c3 Rc8 12. Bd2 Nd5 13. Rc1 e6 14. g4 {with chances for kingside
